data.title: Search local TD using your home address
data.meta_description: Find and contact your local TDs (Teachta Dála) in Ireland. Easily email or tweet all representatives in your constituency. View Dáil vote results and breakdowns by party. Enter your address to get started.
data.meta_site_name: Contact Your Local TD | Who is My TD | Find My TD
